This recipe is perfect for the salmon lover. For all of the people who reviewed it with "fishy" or "bad texture"; free your mind. A salmon cake is just that- a cake made of salmon. If you don't care for the "fishy" flavor of salmon perhaps you're buying a low grade of salmon. Perhaps the salmon you've had in the past was grossly overcooked and therefore had little flavor. Don't criticize a recipe because of it's content when the contents are clear and very well complement themselves. A true culinarian can recognize a good recipe whether he or she likes it or not. This is a good recipe. It is simple in content and execution. The best recipes are often the simplest.

